4.name: Pumpkin Latte
4.description: This lovable chunky monkey is Pumpkin. She's a great family pet, she loves kids and meeting new people!

5.name: Bonus
5.description: This fun fella is Bonus, he loves big yards where he can run! Bonus is great with kids and gets very excited to meet new people. Bonus loves playing tug of war with his rope, but he isn't the biggest fan of fetch.

6.name: Priya
6.description: This is beautiful girl is Priya. She loves meeting new people and is always full of energy. Priya loves families and is very active. Priya loves running around playing fetch and stealing pillows off the couch!
